{"_id": "review-90d00bfb-d95e-40d4-b3bc-5bd07cc08610", "_type": "appReview", "userName": "Abdullah Zubair", "avatarUrl": "https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgk4jjl_koF25lcYqL-MTrfMwIYY3N6YMdC0qEIAZ88MjjUg=mo", "text": "The Mahaana app shows promise, but needs improvements in accessibility. As a visually impaired user, I found these issues with TalkBack: 1. Login button isn't properly clickable with screen reader 2. Unlabeled button for 'Move Funds' in the main interface 3. \"Explore by Touch\" feature isn't supported 4. Frequent automatic logouts I've sent detailed feedback via email. Looking forward to seeing these accessibility features implemented to make the app inclusive for all users. Cheers, Abdullah", "rating": 5, "date": "2025-02-18T07:59:56.000Z"}
